data.description: Experience the epitome of modern luxury in this exquisite 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom townhome in the prestigious ATLANTICA ISLES community in Beachwalk. This natural gas paradise offers unparalleled access to a 14-acre Crystal Clear Lagoon and a host of resort-style amenities. Here's your chance to indulge in the lifestyle you've always dreamed of! Step inside and be captivated by the elegance that defines this home. The interior boasts luxurious touches, including ceramic tile throughout the downstairs and wood floors upstairs. The entire home has been impeccably maintained, presenting itself in pristine, like-new condition.The floor plan is designed for spaciousness and openness, creating an inviting atmosphere that's perfect for both relaxation and entertaining. The master bathroom has This home has been upgraded with ceramic tile for added sophistication and comfort. A standout feature is the stunning iron stair railing, adding architectural artistry to the interior. The gourmet kitchen, a chef's dream, features granite countertops and natural gas for a stylish and functional space. Don't miss your chance to own a slice of paradise in this exclusive community where luxury and leisure effortlessly meet. For a private showing or more information, contact us today to experience the ATLANTICA ISLES lifestyle for yourself!
